      "title": "Australian HC present credentials",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "COLOMBO (News 1st); The Australian High Commissioner Paul Stephens was honored to present credentials to Sri Lankan President Ranil Wickremesinghe yesterday (17).",
        "The High Commissioner said that he looks forward to working together with our valued Sri Lankan partners to further strengthen the bilateral relationship.",
        "Sri Lanka: Inflation will peak in September and trend down \u2013 CBSL Governor",
        "Restructuring domestic debt would lead to an issue \u2013 CBSL Chief"
